title: Sidewall, ca. 1875
creditline: Gift of Edith and Maude Wetmore
description: Full width, giving slightly more than one repeat of slender vine pattern of conventionalized passion-flowers, against secondary all-over pattern of foliation. Paper embossed with a pebble figure.
